        "releaseNotes": "\ud83d\udcf1 Android App Enhancements\r\n\u2022\r\nSmart Deep Linking \ud83d\udd17: Your app is now officially linked to your website. When a user clicks a mystoreapp.pages.dev link, the Android app opens automatically to the exact app page without asking \"Open with Browser?\".\r\n\u2022\r\nOfficial SHA-256 Verification \ud83d\udd11: We integrated your unique digital fingerprint. This makes your app \"Verified\" by the Android system, enabling seamless \"Open by Default\" behavior.\r\n\r\nUniversal Web-Link Sharing \ud83d\udce4: When you share an app from the Android UI, it now generates a professional web link. This ensures that even users who don't have the app can view the details on your website.\r\n\r\nUpdated Brand Identity \ud83c\udd94: All share links in the Profile and Settings have been updated from the old domain to your new official mystoreapp.pages.dev domain.\r\n\ud83c\udf10 Web Ecosystem & Integrations\r\n\r\nPremium \"Plus Jakarta\" UI \u2728: The entire website now uses the high-end Plus Jakarta Sans font with a modern, vertical card-based layout for a professional \"App Store\" feel.\r\n\r\nSecure Blob Download System \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f: We implemented an advanced download logic. Instead of redirecting to GitHub, the browser now fetches the file directly, ensuring 100% full downloads on mobile without any page jumps.\r\n\r\nChrome Security trust-Badge \ud83d\udee1\ufe0f: Added a professional \"Safety Section\" with original Chrome and Play Store icons. This explains to users that the \"File might be harmful\" warning is normal, building trust.\r\n\r\nMobile Redirect Fix \ud83d\udcf1: Fixed a major bug where mobile users were getting stuck on GitHub landing pages. Now, clicking \"Download\" triggers the file transfer immediately.\r\n\r\nDynamic SEO Slugs \ud83d\udcc2: Every app now has a unique, clean URL (e.g., /details/com.music.app) making it easy to share and index on search engines.",
